{"tid":1849974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其批鬥程班長同阿布泰，點解唔攞呢種憤怒去包圍黑心藥房？","createTime":"2020-01-29T10:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T19:00:33.000Z","uid":109462,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cc65d2f1ee02a678e1ad62f746a9f6e65fd9cc3a","tid":1849974,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"一斗米養恩人，一石米養仇人。人性貪心不足就係咁醜陋。<br />\n<br />\n但令到市面口罩咁緊缺嘅責任並不在程班長或者阿布泰呢啲願意同香港市民共渡時艱嘅有心人，而係刻意囤積炒賣、甚至賣假貨嘅黑心藥房，同埋唔肯封關、收埋啲懲教口罩唔放俾市民嘅香港政府。<br />\n<br />\n既然有呢種憤怒去指責程班長、包圍阿布泰，點解呢班人唔去包圍黑心藥房攞啲口罩出嚟派街坊？點解唔去包圍香港政府要佢哋立即封關同埋釋放庫存？"},{"pid":"e4941cc964553c976e91cd2f457482056c976b3b","tid":1849974,"uid":34869,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"批鬥果班根本係藍絲黎"},{"pid":"d40828e3ff3d74781dd1647d60c1365a708b6b77","tid":1849974,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4941cc964553c976e91cd2f457482056c976b3b","tid":1849974,"uid":34869,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"批鬥果班根本係藍絲黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf182e7db7709b7039bdc1888ec5ac5c83466ca","tid":1849974,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"on9樓豬唔撚係以為屌鳩呢2個既人係黃呀嘛???<br />\n不如你為環保出一份力，死撚左去好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c007ee1967b22a5a4a7bdb886bfcb00fe8325145","tid":1849974,"uid":205346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得係同路人批鬥佢地嘅呢？"},{"pid":"eabef6a45a65902972d093c2c1c1183f530c414e","tid":1849974,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c007ee1967b22a5a4a7bdb886bfcb00fe8325145","tid":1849974,"uid":205346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:19:05.000Z","ms